---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Terminal, Heart, Zap, Shield, ArrowRight } from 'lucide-astro';
---

<Layout title="About Empower | The Story">
  
  <section class="relative bg-[#0A0F2C] text-white pt-32 pb-20 px-6 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-purple-900/20 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>
    
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto relative z-10">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-pink-500/10 border border-pink-500/20 text-pink-400 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-8">
        <Terminal class="w-4 h-4" />
        The Founder's Logic
      </div>
      
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-7xl font-bold font-heading mb-8 leading-tight">
        We don't just build websites. <br />
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 to-purple-500">
          We engineer independence.
        </span>
      </h1>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 text-lg text-slate-300 font-body leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          <strong>I started as a Virtual Assistant.</strong> I saw brilliant female founders drowning in admin, fighting with generic software that didn't fit their business, and losing hours to manual data entry.
        </p>
        <p>
          I realised that "hiring help" wasn't the only answer. <strong>Better code was.</strong> So I stopped just managing the chaos and started engineering the solution. Today, Empower Digital Solutions builds bespoke architecture for businesses ready to scale.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-slate-950 py-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        
        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-8 rounded-2xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors group">
          <div class="bg-purple-900/30 p-4 rounded-xl w-fit mb-6 text-purple-400 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
            <Shield class="w-8 h-8" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 font-heading">Supportive Authority</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400">
            We walk a fine line: Expert enough to charge for premium results, but human enough to talk to. No "Tech Bro" condescension. Just clear, unwavering expertise in your corner.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-8 rounded-2xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors group">
          <div class="bg-pink-900/30 p-4 rounded-xl w-fit mb-6 text-pink-400 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
            <Heart class="w-8 h-8" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 font-heading">Trauma-Informed Design</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400">
            Software shouldn't induce anxiety. We build "Calm Technology", systems designed to reduce cognitive load, not add to it. Your dashboard should feel like a sanctuary, not a cockpit.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-8 rounded-2xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors group">
          <div class="bg-blue-900/30 p-4 rounded-xl w-fit mb-6 text-blue-400 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
            <Zap class="w-8 h-8" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 font-heading">Code, Not Config</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400">
            We don't rely on 50 WordPress plugins held together by hope. We write custom, clean code (Next.js, Astro, React) that belongs to you. Fast, secure, and unhackable.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0A0F2C] to-slate-900 py-24 px-6 border-t border-white/5">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
      
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 aspect-[3/4] bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden relative border border-white/10 shadow-2xl rotate-3 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-500">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-purple-900/80 to-transparent z-10"></div>
        <img src="/images/portfolio.jpg" alt="Nicola Berry" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80" />
      </div>

      <div class="w-full md:w-2/3">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6 font-heading">
          "Your independence is your superpower."
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 text-slate-300 font-body">
          <p>
            I built Empower Digital Solutions because I got tired of seeing brilliant business owners held back by bad tech. 
            You shouldn't need a PhD to update your website, and you shouldn't be afraid that your booking system will crash if you get too popular.
          </p>
          <p>
            When you work with me, you aren't hiring an agency that outsources your code to a random server farm. 
            You get <strong>me</strong> building a digital asset that you actually own.
          </p>
          
          <div class="pt-4">
            <p class="font-bold text-white text-lg">Nicola Berry</p>
            <p class="text-purple-400 text-sm font-mono">Lead Engineer & Founder</p>
          </div>

          <div class="pt-8">
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white text-purple-900 px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-purple-100 transition-colors">
              Let's Build Something Real <ArrowRight class="w-4 h-4" />
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
